T3 Code currently has a binary light/dark theme toggle (`useTheme.ts`) with `Theme = "light" | "dark" | "system"` stored in localStorage. The task extends this to a named multi-theme system with 3 built-in themes (`t3-dark`, `t3-light`, `t3-midnight`), each with semantic color tokens for background, foreground, accent, sidebar, editor, terminal, and status bar. A `ThemeProvider` component and `ThemeSelector` UI with color swatches are also required.

